data.description: No guest is left out in the rain with this grand front and back covered porches. Walking through the foyer into a beautiful, open, split floor plan with a light, airy pallet, and windows bookending a gas fireplace with mantle, you immediately feel relaxed at home where entertaining is a breeze.  Enjoy your refreshments while resting on the large rear covered patio overlooking the pond.  This home boasts an oversize main bedroom overlooking the serene pond with one spare room near and 2 spare bedrooms on the opposite side of the home.  In keeping your home tidy the oversized mudroom is ready for book sacks, brief cases and shoes with an adjacent, huge laundry room.  Book your tour today for this home won't last long.
